Darkrai (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0490: Manaphy
Pokémon
#0492: Shaymin →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Darkrai (TCG Pocket).

Darkrai has been featured on 24 different cards since it debuted in the Great Encounters expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Darkrai cards are normally Darkness-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Darkrai

Darkrai

Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
